{"tid":2128015,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國於少女像前設立安倍下跪雕像，主題為「永遠的贖罪」","createTime":"2020-07-27T16:03:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T16:52:24.000Z","uid":73883,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"82a8d3cb16a3905037ce73d39dd0156fde363000","tid":2128015,"uid":73883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T16:03:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.kyodonews.net/chinese/public/images/posts/c173cd20c90424f2639c7bee27d44333/photo_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.kyodonews.net%2Fchinese%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fposts%2Fc173cd20c90424f2639c7bee27d44333%2Fphoto_l.jpg&h=5e634052&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【共同社首爾7月27日電】位於韓國東北部江原道平昌的私立&ldquo;韓國自生植物園&rdquo;日前在園內設置了象徵慰安婦問題的少女像，還有在少女像前下跪謝罪的以日本首相安倍晉三為原型的雕像。據稱主題為&ldquo;永遠的贖罪&rdquo;。園長在接受韓國《京鄉新聞》採訪等場合透露了該消息。<br />\n<br />\n網上除了來自日本的批評外，韓國國內也意見不一，引起爭議。園長27日接受共同社採訪時表示：&ldquo;不是針對安倍製作的，而是象徵著處於謝罪立場的所有男性。也可能是少女的父親。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n園長還主張稱，&ldquo;雕像是自己花錢製作的植物園擺設，沒有政治目的&rdquo;。原本計劃8月舉行揭幕儀式，但已取消。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tchina.kyodonews.net/news/2020/07/cb47ec193ac0.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftchina.kyodonews.net%2Fnews%2F2020%2F07%2Fcb47ec193ac0.html&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBnRNzM9MViFDfs2457H6WAQ%3D&h=fdb9c768\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tchina.kyodonews.net/news/2020/07/cb47ec193ac0.html</a>"},{"pid":"4fdc3da50b43feb2126affc9f5c5933ef5447a81","tid":2128015,"uid":20170,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T16:06:45.000Z","msg":"講撚明晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同中國人一樣"},{"pid":"916c69c72aadc11b5978529c6c77458a111be8be","tid":2128015,"uid":73883,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T16:20:03.000Z","msg":"自己打飛機，同某國差無幾，唉...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"756155ca8b9ca3f54ce3854644e25c6aa73bc0b8","tid":2128015,"uid":147721,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"cite